# Vercel Blob — required for artwork save/share in production.
# 1. Go to vercel.com/~/stores → Create Blob Store (use Public access).
# 2. Connect the store to this project in the Storage tab.
# 3. Run `vercel env pull .env.local` to populate locally, or copy the token
#    manually from the store dashboard → Settings → Tokens.
BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=
